BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Finn: A New Musical – at the PB&J Cafe
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260501T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260501T203000
UID:bat-202605011830-finn-a-new-musical-at-the-pb-j-cafe@bloomingtonarts.t
 oday
DESCRIPTION:$. From the creator of Doc McStuffins and Vampirina\, Finn is 
 a heartwarming musical adventure about a young shark on the brink of growi
 ng up. As he prepares to join the fearsome Shark Guard\, Finn can’t shak
 e the feeling that he’s different from the other sharks. Deep inside\, h
 e discovers a colorful fish inside him—a part of himself that longs to s
 parkle\, sing\, and dance. As Finn embarks on a journey of self-discovery\
 , friendship\, and adventure\, he finds the courage to be himself! Fun for
  all ages!
LOCATION:Waldron Auditorium @ Waldron Arts Center
URL:https://seeconstellation.org/kids/finn/
X-SOURCE:BloomingtonArts.Today
END:VEVENT
