BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Sluice
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260503T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260503T220000
UID:bat-202605032000-sluice@bloomingtonarts.today
DESCRIPTION:$. Sluice returns with *Companion*\, a record about losing fai
 th in the dream of music—and finding it again. Led by Justin Morris\, th
 e Durham four-piece channels indie rock\, country-tinged choruses\, and sp
 iritual reflection into songs about love\, labor\, and second chances. It
 ’s a story of disillusionment turned into determination\, where music be
 comes not escape or stardom\, but companionship.
LOCATION:The Bishop Bar
URL:https://www.thebishopbar.com/events/sluice
X-SOURCE:BloomingtonArts.Today
END:VEVENT
